Print Squares
Write a program that utilizes a while loop to print the squares of numbers from 1 to 
N
N.

Check the sample input / output below further clarity.

Sample 1:
Input
Output
5
1 4 9 16 25
CODE:
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int N;
    // Reading the value of N
    cin >> N;

    int i = 1;
    // Use a while loop to iterate from 1 to N
    while (i <= N) {
        // Calculate the square and print it followed by a space
        cout << i * i << " ";
        i++; // Increment the counter
    }

    cout << endl; // Print a newline at the end
    return 0;
}
